ichtsbarkeit. Seine Untersuchung der zeitgenössischen Publizistik macht deutlich, dass das frühe 18. Jahrhundert eine Phase des Medienwandels hin zu einem verstärkten Gebrauch der Druckmedien war.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aConflict managementzGermany. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978305004939740uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978305005593040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050055930423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783050055930/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OGSc2005d2012